We pray a hedge of protection around and about them, over every party, every get-together, and any kind of celebration.

01:38:50.719 --> 01:39:09.718
We pray a hedge of protection that his Secret Service is more attentive, even to the ones in the room just because they passed security.

01:39:09.719 --> 01:39:45.531
I don't understand it in the natural, but we thank you, Lord, that President Trump is protected.

01:39:45.532 --> 01:40:23.782
No weapon formed against him shall prosper. Every plot and plan will be uncovered in the name of Jesus, even at black-tie events.

01:40:23.783 --> 01:41:11.883
We pray over Don Jr. in the name of Jesus. The blood of Jesus surrounds him.

01:41:11.884 --> 01:41:19.639
He will finish his course; he will live long and finish strong.

01:41:19.640 --> 01:41:29.999
We pray over his heart, over every artery, and over the valves of the heart.

01:41:30.000 --> 01:41:51.575
We call for protection in the name of Jesus over his food and drinks.

01:41:51.576 --> 01:42:17.761
I believe we can pray over his drinks, the goblet, and everything that is ever handed to him.

01:42:17.762 --> 01:42:25.399
You said we could eat or drink any deadly thing and it would not harm us.

01:42:25.400 --> 01:43:14.119
Everything he eats and drinks is protected in any place, any palace, or any country.

01:43:14.120 --> 01:43:46.639
I pray that any kind of poison or any attempt to make it look like a natural accident fails.

01:43:46.640 --> 01:43:58.599
Every plot, every plan, and every pursuit is uncovered. I thank you, Lord, that you protect President Trump and raise a hedge around him.

01:43:58.600 --> 01:44:08.436
I thank you that his Secret Service members are so heightened and alert; they never let their guard down.

01:44:08.437 --> 01:44:17.079
They are like bulldogs, always watching everyone's hands and those bringing refreshments.

01:44:17.080 --> 01:44:48.319
They are smart, watching over what he eats and drinks. He has food tasters, whatever—we protect him in the name of Jesus.

01:44:48.320 --> 01:45:06.759
Thank you, Father, for our president. He has much more to do, and you have mercy on him.

01:45:06.760 --> 01:45:23.679
Draw him close to you in the midnight hour. He, his marriage, and his kids need refreshing.

01:45:23.680 --> 01:45:36.159
They've had a hard road, and I ask you to give them supernatural sleep.

01:45:36.160 --> 01:45:56.399
I pray over Don Jr., Eric, and the kids. I thank you for the angels that watch over them. You said you were going to double their money.

01:45:56.400 --> 01:46:04.059
I saw a doubling and tripling of Eric Trump's investments concerning everything the devil stole.

01:46:04.060 --> 01:46:20.256
He's going to restore it back double and triple in Jesus'name. The Lord says you can move on; we have covered that.

01:46:20.257 --> 01:47:31.394
There is something concerning Venezuela; that's where we're headed now.

01:47:31.395 --> 01:48:05.159
There is an escalation of things, like in Iraq, a removing and pulling down of governments.

01:48:05.160 --> 01:48:32.094
Look for an increase. They are looking for an opportunity, and you see Putin coming to the aid.

01:48:32.095 --> 01:49:03.820
It's about BRICS. They're playing chess; it's 3D or 4D. People need to realize they are just trying to outwait his term. They think they can bypass this for three years.

01:49:03.821 --> 01:50:21.714
They don't think about Jesus coming; they're just thinking, 'How do we get through until he's gone?'They have a plan that's beyond his term, looking into 2028 and beyond.

01:50:21.715 --> 01:52:03.839
Church, use this opportunity. Fall of 2027 is circled. These evil men—I see Xi Jinping—think if it worked once, it'll work again.

01:52:03.840 --> 01:53:03.799
Glory to God, the church has victory. We must pray for the fall of 2027, November and December. The church must use the opportunity I've given them today.

01:53:03.800 --> 01:53:48.599
I see the church rising, but it's a different world than what you can imagine, coming out of great sorrow, pressure, and civil unrest.

01:53:48.600 --> 01:54:27.759
We pray over our president and his decisions. I see the number 2032.

01:54:27.760 --> 01:55:07.286
It instantaneously skipped from 2028 to 2032, and 2032 is highlighted.

01:55:07.287 --> 01:55:41.279
That's a four-year term window. He only shows me what He wants to show me.

01:55:41.280 --> 01:56:30.596
I had a vision in 2023 of the clouds, and I'm seeing them again. It stopped and I am not allowed to get into 2028 and 2029.

01:56:30.597 --> 01:56:51.429
There is something going on in this timeframe; it is like a cloud. The Lord said, "Go back to Kim, Braden.

01:56:51.430 --> 01:57:09.239
The vision of Kim in 2027 and 2028."There is something around this, and I have to call Donna and ask her.

01:57:09.240 --> 01:57:31.305
2028 is highlighted; it is about the church. I see electricity and bolts of lightning coming out of a cloud.

01:57:31.306 --> 01:58:07.319
I see a major storm coming, a very bad storm. What will you do with the time that I have given you?

01:58:07.320 --> 01:59:49.999
For a storm is coming again. What have you done, church? What will you do with the time I have given you?

01:59:50.000 --> 02:00:30.879
Why do I see Billie Eilish at the Super Bowl? Why do I see this young girl? I see events coming; they are coming.

02:00:30.880 --> 02:00:50.115
The storm is even revolving around people in an auditorium, a football stadium like the Super Bowl.

02:00:50.116 --> 02:01:18.144
I see people with their phones. It is an open dome. There is great witchcraft here, some kind of demonic presence.

02:01:18.145 --> 02:01:54.254
I have been praying for this girl's salvation, that she would be radically born again and have a visitation from Him.

02:01:54.255 --> 02:02:45.965
I see Kim Clement's face, lightning, and a cloud. Time is running out.

02:02:45.966 --> 02:03:59.759
I hear the Father say, "Time is running out."When I get to 2028, I see a bad storm, but the view is blocked past that into 2029.

02:03:59.760 --> 02:05:17.599
There is a wall there. Arise, church! I see a whirlwind, a cloud, and lightning.

02:05:17.600 --> 02:06:46.592
Why do I see Kim Clement playing his piano? I see a four-year window here; I keep seeing 2032 highlighted.

02:06:46.593 --> 02:08:18.199
The storm is around 2027 and 2028. What will you do with this window of time? I extended it, but what will you do with it?

02:08:18.200 --> 02:08:42.119
I see Trump in a boat, paddling against a current called the Great Depression. He is fighting to keep America from going over a waterfall.

02:08:42.120 --> 02:09:21.799
The canoe says "USA"and he is paddling as fast as he can to keep the boat from going over the edge.

02:09:21.800 --> 02:09:57.279
I am giving you more time. What have you done with it so far? I see an hourglass and the sand is going through it.

02:09:57.280 --> 02:11:01.620
I saw a football stadium with no roof. Maybe it was not the Super Bowl, but it was a massive football stadium.

02:11:01.621 --> 02:11:21.692
I do not want to automatically assume it is the Super Bowl, but it looked like that.

02:11:21.693 --> 02:11:39.170
The lights and the party atmosphere made it look like a Super Bowl.

02:11:39.171 --> 02:11:48.236
Billie Eilish was wearing a white shirt and dancing low to the ground; it was very demonic.

02:11:48.238 --> 02:12:51.919
I saw a whirlwind and heard a storm. I saw Kim Clement playing his piano with electricity around him.

02:12:51.920 --> 02:13:34.702
We must pray for President Trump, for his heart, his health, and his protection.

02:13:34.703 --> 02:13:49.947
I saw a beautiful black-tie event with feathers in the centerpieces and women in sequin dresses. I was there in the spirit today.

02:13:49.948 --> 02:14:29.059
I was talking to you, but I was so deep into the vision that I had to have Diana hold me to keep me grounded.

02:14:29.060 --> 02:14:59.032
I can smell it and taste it. It sounds weird in the natural, but I go to the future in the spirit and I see a storm.

02:14:59.033 --> 02:15:09.519
I see all these things coming, but it stopped around Xi Jinping, and they're going to release another virus.

02:15:09.520 --> 02:15:21.719
They're going to do something to try to derail the election in 2028. I saw a major plan to derail the election in 2028.

02:15:21.720 --> 02:15:37.559
And if we don't pray for the church going into 2028, I saw a lot of people die and I was there.

02:15:37.560 --> 02:15:52.159
The storm is beyond anybody's comprehension. We must pray for the church on this channel and intercede for what I just saw.

02:15:52.160 --> 02:16:08.039
2020, 2027, 2028—we must pray because it will make COVID look like a walk in the park.

02:16:08.040 --> 02:16:34.239
2029, I couldn't see past; it was a black line, but then it skipped and there were clouds, and I could see these clouds—kind of like after a storm, kind of like when you're looking into a storm—but then it went clear to 2032 and it was circled too.

02:16:34.240 --> 02:16:38.286
I don't know why, but the numbers were highlighted before me.

02:16:38.287 --> 02:16:44.908
I'm not saying the rapture is not taking place, because you'll have these people getting mad and throwing eggs at me.

02:16:44.909 --> 02:16:50.558
I'm not saying that. I don't know why I saw what I saw. I don't know yet.

02:16:50.559 --> 02:17:02.602
But I've seen it again, and I've been there before. My son has a record of it in 2023.

02:17:02.603 --> 02:17:17.678
I went there before and I haven't been there since. December 16th, 2023, I went there.

02:17:17.679 --> 02:17:24.159
But when I go out that far like that, it's just really wild for me.

02:17:24.160 --> 02:17:33.239
I'm just telling y'all, there are days of heaven on earth for the body of Christ because I could see the glorious church in all this.

02:17:33.240 --> 02:17:43.279
I could see the church operating like a church, but it comes out of great pressure.

02:17:43.280 --> 02:17:50.119
The church right now is a bunch of babies compared to what I saw coming.

02:17:50.120 --> 02:17:59.239
And you think, 'Well, everything is great, Brandon, because we're going to get out of here for the rapture of the church.'You are wrong.

02:17:59.240 --> 02:18:04.037
You are wrong. And I believe in the rapture more than 99.9% of you.

02:18:04.038 --> 02:18:07.693
But there is a shaking that comes before the rapture, and it's about to happen.

02:18:07.694 --> 02:18:16.039
I'm telling you all, you need to get your cup full. You don't want to hear that, but I'm telling you the truth.

02:18:16.040 --> 02:18:21.720
There's a shaking. There's a storm. It's not church usual; it's church unusual.

02:18:21.721 --> 02:18:32.119
And you're going to see the people come out of a slumber; they've all been asleep, and the church is going to get woken up.

02:18:32.120 --> 02:18:36.799
You're going to see a shaking to awaken, and people are not going to want...

02:18:36.800 --> 02:18:56.239
it's not church usual. It felt like the Great Depression around me when I was in it. It felt to me like a financial Armageddon.

02:18:56.240 --> 02:19:01.096
It felt like the church—there were certain people that had the money, but I could feel the darkness.

02:19:01.097 --> 02:19:08.359
I could feel the sadness. It was heavy. I could feel the heaviness.

02:19:08.360 --> 02:19:12.319
And the church was rising. There was a Pentecostal church. It was glorious.

02:19:12.320 --> 02:19:19.728
People were coming to Jesus by the tens of thousands. They were coming because people were desperate.

02:19:19.729 --> 02:19:25.130
They were scared. It was a shaking—earthquakes, signs in the heavens.

02:19:25.131 --> 02:19:43.999
You're seeing it. We're at the beginning of sorrows. We've not seen things like this—what we're about to see. I'm done tonight. I'm tired now.

02:19:44.000 --> 02:20:10.039
But it hits you hard because you see people and you see it all going into the future like that and I just go, 'Oh no.'The world is...

02:20:10.040 --> 02:20:17.628
the only way I can describe it to you is I see lots of purples and I see lots of colors like that on the people and in the sound.

02:20:17.629 --> 02:20:20.559
I was in England. I was going through England. I could see Europe.

02:20:20.560 --> 02:20:30.559
I was going through Europe. I could see war. I could see things happening so fast as I was traveling along.

02:20:30.560 --> 02:20:38.576
I'm not able to communicate it to you by words. I'm praying and I'm seeing things, and I tell you little things, but it's all happening so fast.

02:20:38.577 --> 02:20:52.153
It's like I'm going through a speed and it's just flying by. And that's why I say I keep seeing Kim Clement, and he was there, praying and playing his piano, but he's been dead since 2015.

02:20:52.154 --> 02:21:04.359
He passed away. Why am I seeing this man praying around? Is he in the great cloud of witnesses praying for 2027, 2028?

02:21:04.360 --> 02:21:15.039
I don't know. But he was at the base of the storm and he was playing. He was praying and he was prophesying in 2027, 2028.

02:21:15.040 --> 02:21:26.664
He was prophesying, and he was playing his piano, and I could hear him singing 'The Mountain of the Lord.'It was moving, a move of God, but he was praying and he was prophesying over 2028 and 2027.

02:21:26.665 --> 02:21:39.610
It was like he was still here, but he's not. I was like, 'Why is he at the base of these years?'Because I could see the years ahead above his head, and he was praying into that timeframe for America.

02:21:39.611 --> 02:21:55.871
He must be praying in heaven, interceding. Something's happening in the great cloud of witnesses, like I saw with Lucy and with Sister Wilkerson; they were interceding for Minnesota.

02:21:55.872 --> 02:22:17.799
But this time I saw Kim Clement praying into that storm. He had a red shirt on.

02:22:17.800 --> 02:22:44.879
He looked really nice, young. I pray the Lord keeps me safe and protects me and my wife and my children.

02:22:44.880 --> 02:22:56.519
Thank you, Lord, for all that you do for us. I pray the church wakes up.

02:22:56.520 --> 02:23:14.039
I pray you get serious and full of God and He becomes real to you.

02:23:14.040 --> 02:23:26.599
God bless you all. If you don't know my friend Jesus, you must know Jesus.

02:23:26.600 --> 02:23:30.528
It's appointed unto man once to die and after that the judgment.

02:23:30.529 --> 02:23:45.999
If you've never accepted Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal savior, you must know Him. If you've never confessed Jesus, tonight's your night.

02:23:46.000 --> 02:23:53.501
I know this to an unbeliever probably is way out there, but I'm telling you, there are realms of the spirit.

02:23:53.502 --> 02:24:08.239
There are places with the Holy Spirit where He will become your best friend. But you must know Him.

02:24:08.240 --> 02:24:22.563
Or you could be one of the ones watching right now who used to be on fire for the Lord, but you got mad at the church and turned your back on God.

02:24:22.564 --> 02:24:27.729
You've been backslidden. God's never turned His back on you; you turned your back on Him.

02:24:27.730 --> 02:24:37.658
But tonight's the night He wants you to come home. I'm going to say a simple prayer right now.

02:24:37.659 --> 02:25:03.940
If you're saying, 'Brandon, you're talking to me; I just want to know Jesus,'I want you to get bold about your faith and say in the comment section, 'I want to be saved.'It's appointed unto man once to die.

02:25:03.941 --> 02:25:08.679
Like I told you, you don't know the day you're going to die. None of us do.

02:25:08.680 --> 02:25:33.472
The undertaker might be taking your shoes off tonight. No one's promised tomorrow.

02:25:33.473 --> 02:25:45.919
Say this simple prayer after me: 'Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

02:25:45.920 --> 02:25:55.519
I believe that you died for me and you rose again on the third day.'Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a savior.

02:25:55.520 --> 02:26:04.079
I ask you to forgive me of my sins. I ask you to cleanse me of all of my unrighteousness, all the bad I've done.

02:26:04.080 --> 02:26:09.199
I confess it before you right now and I ask you to forgive me of it.

02:26:09.200 --> 02:26:16.438
Jesus, wash me. Make me new. Jesus, tonight I turn my back on the world.

02:26:16.439 --> 02:26:25.839
I turn my back on the devil. From this day forward, I serve you. I'm sold out to you, Lord.

02:26:25.840 --> 02:26:31.799
I ask you to forgive me and I thank you, Lord, that today is a new start.

02:26:31.800 --> 02:26:41.439
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. Thank you, Lord. Thank you, Lord, that I'm saved.

02:26:41.440 --> 02:26:48.079
Thank you, Lord, that today is my new beginning. In the name of Jesus. Amen and amen.

02:26:48.080 --> 02:26:53.279
Well, if you just said that prayer, I believe that you got born again.

02:26:53.280 --> 02:27:03.354
I believe that today is a new beginning. What do you do? You go to a non-denominational church after this. I'd find a non-denominational church.

02:27:03.355 --> 02:27:09.214
Tell that pastor, 'I just got born again on the internet and I need to be water baptized.'Get baptized and plug into that church.

02:27:09.215 --> 02:27:14.293
Go to church on Sundays. Go to church on Wednesdays. Whatever you can do to get plugged in there. Volunteer.

02:27:14.294 --> 02:27:21.599
Do whatever you can to learn about Christianity and what you've done today to accept Jesus Christ in your decision.

02:27:21.600 --> 02:27:30.673
Read your Bible every single day. Pray and come here and pray with us. If you don't have a Bible, we'll buy you your first Bible.

02:27:30.674 --> 02:27:41.198
If you can't afford a Bible, if you don't have a Bible, we want to celebrate your decision tonight to give Jesus Christ your heart to serve the Lord with all your heart from this day forward.

02:27:41.199 --> 02:27:48.077
We want to celebrate your decision tonight by giving you your first free Bible.

02:27:48.078 --> 02:27:58.867
I want you to go to the description where you'll see our email address.

02:27:58.868 --> 02:28:11.879
If you just put in the title 'I just got saved'and your name and address, we will get a Bible to you in the mail just to say congratulations.

02:28:11.880 --> 02:28:15.666
So we want to love on you and thank you for joining us again tonight.

02:28:15.667 --> 02:28:21.995
I don't know how many got saved tonight, but we pray somebody did. And if you did, we rejoice with you.

02:28:21.996 --> 02:28:26.756
And if not, there'll be probably some later on watching this and get saved.

02:28:26.757 --> 02:28:35.959
But we had 43 so far who got saved is what it said. Ain't that interesting? It's always this 43-some-odd people.

02:28:35.960 --> 02:28:40.998
Glory to God for every single one of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ.

02:28:40.999 --> 02:28:46.438
We pray that this video richly blessed you and this stirred you up.

02:28:46.439 --> 02:28:56.260
If you could, we never ask you to do anything, but we do ask you to do this: like, subscribe, and comment down below something nice.

02:28:56.261 --> 02:29:02.359
If this video blessed you tonight, let us know. It blessed me.

02:29:02.360 --> 02:29:11.159
I'll be real with you; it troubled me in the natural a little bit about what I saw coming, but I know that God has us, and he'll never leave us.

02:29:11.160 --> 02:29:16.176
He'll never forsake us. We need to keep our eyes on Jesus. There's a lot going on.

02:29:16.177 --> 02:29:23.885
So, we're excited you came tonight. I pray. Do they have any questions at all?

02:29:23.886 --> 02:29:34.531
They're saying in the Bronx in New York, they're positive that the van caught fire.

02:29:34.532 --> 02:29:44.439
That's not good, for what I've seen is just the beginning. I saw New York burning.

02:29:44.440 --> 02:29:54.615
I saw it burning everywhere, so much so that it looked like something out of a bad movie. There were fires burning everywhere.

02:29:54.616 --> 02:30:02.586
The big buildings were burning, and it looked like something out of a—it was terrible, what I saw coming to New York.

02:30:02.587 --> 02:30:09.759
The Lord said, 'Go back to David Wilkerson's prophecy about the fires and the things coming to New York.

02:30:09.760 --> 02:30:19.799
All these years they've been delayed.'And you may think I'm really a negative person, but I am not.

02:30:19.800 --> 02:30:31.279
I am not. I'm a very positive person. But I have to tell you what I see.

02:30:31.280 --> 02:30:41.833
Out of things that you choose, out of people's choices, they'll get what they wanted, but they won't like what they get.

02:30:41.834 --> 02:30:46.117
You'll get what you asked for, but it's not what you thought.

02:30:46.118 --> 02:30:52.559
It's not what you thought. So, there's so many of you here tonight.

02:30:52.560 --> 02:30:57.999
6,000—I don't know if that's still left. 5,000—so, a thousand left.

02:30:58.000 --> 02:31:10.718
Quite a few left. Well, now the call comes, but that's it. Well, God bless you all.

02:31:10.719 --> 02:31:22.479
Remember, we love you and we will see you again tomorrow. More than likely, tomorrow is our Thursday. I try to keep praying with y'all.

02:31:22.480 --> 02:31:31.438
I dedicate this time for you to pray with you and to see what the Lord wants to tell you what's coming outside of our own personal prayer time.

02:31:31.439 --> 02:31:38.195
But we're so excited that you're part of it and we're so excited that you're here every time. Thank you for joining us.

02:31:38.196 --> 02:31:44.885
I know it's really late, but it's the time I have to give you after I work and I do all things during the day.

02:31:44.886 --> 02:31:54.319
I told Diana it's harder for me to do it in the earlier part. But we try really hard to make it an effort every day to try to pray with y'all.

02:31:54.320 --> 02:32:04.799
And so we're thankful for every single one of you. And we pray that blessed you and that you got stirred up a little bit or whatever and get refreshed.

02:32:04.800 --> 02:32:12.448
I'm still a little out of it. It's pretty intense tonight for me.

02:32:12.449 --> 02:32:17.303
God bless you all. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:32:17.304 --> 02:32:27.600
Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

